01:26:19.431 --> 01:26:22.411
it's very important.

01:26:25.091 --> 01:26:29.911
Then again you have to put your hand in the upper portion of our abdomen on the left hand side.

01:26:33.291 --> 01:26:37.851
Please all of you have to do it, please all of you do it.

01:26:39.371 --> 01:26:44.371
Now put your right hand on your heart, again.

01:26:49.391 --> 01:26:55.711
Now when you feel guilty the center here

01:26:56.711 --> 01:27:02.991
on, in the corner of your neck and your shoulder, here catches very badly

