01:27:13.271 --> 01:27:20.671
so it's no use being guilty. Now turn your head to your right and press it hard here, as much as you can,

01:27:24.991 --> 01:27:29.531
knowing that you're not guilty in the eyes of God.

01:27:32.211 --> 01:27:37.411
Now, put your right hand on top of your forehead across

01:27:38.351 --> 01:27:46.091
