01:27:46.431 --> 01:27:52.231
and put down your head as far as possible. This is a center to forgive,

01:27:52.531 --> 01:27:55.711
to forgive everyone in general.

01:27:58.811 --> 01:28:06.031
We'll do that later on just now I'm showing you where to put your hand. Now please, take your right hand on the back side of your head

01:28:08.031 --> 01:28:11.011
and push back your head as far as possible.

01:28:15.831 --> 01:28:21.391
This is the center, where without feeling guilty - push back your head as far as possible.

01:28:22.231 --> 01:28:29.311
This is the center where, without feeling guilty, without condemning yourself, without counting your mistakes,

01:28:29.911 --> 01:28:37.211
for your own satisfaction, you have to ask forgiveness from this All-Pervading Divine power of love.

01:28:38.391 --> 01:28:44.271
Now, stretch your hand fully. Now the last center - very important.

01:28:44.891 --> 01:28:52.871
Put the center of your palm on top of the fontanel bone area which was a soft bone in your childhood.

01:28:54.271 --> 01:29:01.931
Put the center properly. Now, push back your fingers - this is for the actualization of the baptism, as they say.

01:29:02.751 --> 01:29:10.671
Push back your fingers so that there's a good pressure on your scalp. Now please put down your head, as far as possible

01:29:12.331 --> 01:29:17.991
and now move your scalp, slowly, clockwise, seven times.

01:29:21.991 --> 01:29:27.911
Please move your scalp slowly, clockwise, seven times. Put down your head.

01:29:28.451 --> 01:29:36.451
This is the last center called as Sahastrara, means the lotus of thousand petals, which covers the limbic area.

01:29:50.951 --> 01:29:54.811
Now, that's all we have to do, that's all.

01:29:56.851 --> 01:30:03.851
You'll have to close your eyes, when I tell you, you can take out your spectacles - later on you can put them on.

01:30:05.831 --> 01:30:13.891
You have to put both your feet apart from each other, as I told you there are two powers separate - one complementary to other.

01:30:14.851 --> 01:30:18.751
Just put both the feet apart from each other. Put the left hand towards Me

01:30:22.911 --> 01:30:26.191
and now put the right hand on your heart.

01:30:27.491 --> 01:30:34.231
Please close your eyes. Put close them slowly, not pressing them down but just

01:30:37.331 --> 01:30:43.771
close them so that the lids are not pressed and compressed.

01:30:44.751 --> 01:30:47.711
Now here

01:30:55.811 --> 01:31:02.951
you have to ask Me a very fundamental question about yourself, three times in your heart.

01:31:05.331 --> 01:31:12.511
Please ask a question within your heart - you can call Me Mother or Shri Mataji whatever you feel like.

01:31:14.531 --> 01:31:21.751
"Mother, am I the Spirit?" ask this question in your heart. "Mother, am I the Spirit?"

01:31:35.571 --> 01:31:43.451
In the heart resides the Spirit and if you are the Spirit, you become your own master, your own guide, your own guru.

01:31:44.091 --> 01:31:51.811
So now, please take down your right hand into the upper portion of your abdomen

01:31:52.311 --> 01:31:55.671
on the left-hand side and press it, not very hard.

01:31:57.291 --> 01:32:01.791
This is the center for the principle of mastery.

01:32:02.411 --> 01:32:07.191
So now, you ask another, very fundamental question in your heart, three times

01:32:08.711 --> 01:32:15.271
"Mother, am I my own master? Mother, am I my own master?"

01:32:15.811 --> 01:32:19.491
Ask this question three times in your heart.

01:32:43.811 --> 01:32:47.611
I've already told you that I respect your freedom

01:32:49.071 --> 01:32:53.851
and I cannot force pure knowledge on you - you have to ask for it.

01:32:54.851 --> 01:32:59.731
So now, please take your right hand in the lower portion of your abdomen on the left-hand side

01:33:00.171 --> 01:33:05.411
and here you have to ask six times because this center has got six petals,

01:33:07.531 --> 01:33:10.631
"Mother, please give me pure knowledge."

01:33:13.811 --> 01:33:18.631
Ask six times, "Mother, please give me pure knowledge."

01:33:25.611 --> 01:33:33.651
As soon as you ask for pure knowledge, your Kundalini starts rising

01:33:36.711 --> 01:33:39.851
and when She starts rising,

01:33:43.831 --> 01:33:47.991
we have to understand that we have to nourish all the centers

01:33:49.771 --> 01:33:55.711
which are upper centers so that it's easy for Her

01:33:57.271 --> 01:34:03.351
to pass through. This has to be done with our self-confidence in ourselves,

01:34:04.691 --> 01:34:11.651
with our self-esteem and knowing what glorious things we are.

01:34:12.891 --> 01:34:17.351
Now raise your right hand in the upper portion of your abdomen and press it hard.

01:34:18.991 --> 01:34:22.011
Here

01:34:27.211 --> 01:34:34.571
you have to say, ten times, with full confidence, "Mother, I am my master."

01:34:37.171 --> 01:34:43.551
Say in your heart, "Mother I am my master, " ten times.

01:34:47.331 --> 01:34:50.331
Press it hard

01:34:56.051 --> 01:35:02.651
Now the fundamental truth about you is that, you're not this body, not this mind,

01:35:03.431 --> 01:35:09.311
not this intellect, nor these conditionings and not your ego -

01:35:09.971 --> 01:35:12.991
you are pure Spirit.

01:35:15.091 --> 01:35:18.171
So now, raise your right hand on your heart

01:35:22.911 --> 01:35:28.451
Here you have to

01:35:29.271 --> 01:35:32.431
say again with full confidence,

01:35:33.371 --> 01:35:40.811
"Mother, I am the Spirit, I am the pure Spirit, " say it twelve times.

01:35:41.431 --> 01:35:45.151
"Mother, I am the pure Spirit."

01:35:47.711 --> 01:35:52.351
This self-confidence will open your hearts, will open your chakras.

01:36:00.291 --> 01:36:08.291
You have to know that this All-Pervading power is the ocean of knowledge, is the ocean of compassion and love,

01:36:08.991 --> 01:36:14.771
is the ocean of bliss but above all it is the ocean of forgiveness

01:36:15.431 --> 01:36:21.331
so whatever you may do wrong, whatever you think was against

01:36:22.751 --> 01:36:27.731
goodness, please forgive just now, forgive yourself,

01:36:29.191 --> 01:36:33.791
completely forgive yourself because all

01:36:34.591 --> 01:36:40.951
these mistakes can be easily dissolved by the power of ocean of forgiveness.

01:36:42.631 --> 01:36:46.151
So now raise your right hand in the corner of your neck

01:36:49.591 --> 01:36:56.951
and, neck and the shoulder and turn your head to your right fully.

01:36:58.951 --> 01:37:04.851
Here, very much with your self-confidence, you have to say sixteen times

01:37:06.131 --> 01:37:11.951
because this center has got sixteen petals, sixteen times with full confidence,

01:37:12.291 --> 01:37:19.871
"Mother, I'm not guilty at all, Mother, I'm not guilty at all."  Whatever people might have told you, forget it.

01:37:20.651 --> 01:37:25.111
"Mother, I'm not guilty at all, " please say it sixteen times.

01:37:30.911 --> 01:37:35.951
I've already told you, whether you forgive or don't forgive,

01:37:36.791 --> 01:37:41.031
you don't do anything. On the contrary you play into wrong hands.

01:37:42.251 --> 01:37:47.431
Those who have tortured you, are not troubled, while you are troubled.

01:37:53.651 --> 01:38:00.491
So you have to forgive all of them. Now raise your hand on your forehead across,

01:38:01.211 --> 01:38:04.251
press it hard on both the sides.

01:38:05.711 --> 01:38:09.131
Please put down your head, please put down your head.

01:38:09.291 --> 01:38:14.771
Here you have to say from your heart, not how many times, from your heart you have to say,

01:38:15.951 --> 01:38:20.311
"Mother, I forgive everyone, in general."

01:38:22.671 --> 01:38:26.691
"Mother, I forgive everyone, in general."

01:38:38.111 --> 01:38:45.591
Please say it from your heart. This center is a very constricted small center on the cross of

01:38:46.811 --> 01:38:52.251
