01:38:54.651 --> 01:39:00.851
Now, put your right hand on the back side of your head

01:39:02.351 --> 01:39:09.031
on the optic lobe, as they call it, and push back your head as far back as possible towards the sky.

01:39:12.011 --> 01:39:19.971
Here, you have to say for your own satisfaction, not counting your mistakes,

01:39:26.671 --> 01:39:34.631
"Oh Divine power, if I have done anything wrong knowingly or unknowingly, please forgive me."

01:39:43.711 --> 01:39:47.691
"Oh Divine power, if I have done anything

01:39:48.591 --> 01:39:51.591
