Now, stretch your hand,

01:40:16.391 --> 01:40:19.471
stretch your palm fully

01:40:24.391 --> 01:40:27.411
and put the center

01:40:28.171 --> 01:40:35.111
of your palm on top of the fontanel bone area, which is a soft bone in your childhood.

01:40:36.491 --> 01:40:42.811
Now, put down your head, as far as possible,  put down your head, as far as possible,

01:40:43.231 --> 01:40:49.591
